Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:07.32,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\shad0\bord2\frz1.5\fs34\t(\fs32)\move(364.797,35,364.797,54,24,7323)\c&&HC9D4D7&}Warning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:03.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Viewers Sitting in Front of the Television,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:05.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,the guys that appear in this anime are delinquents.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.27,0:00:07.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So, please do not imitate what you see in this anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:09.98,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnAveria Sans\b1\i0\bord0\blur0.3\fad(450,0)\c&HDADADA&\fs33\pos(362.532,49)}Do not imitate{\i1\fs40}!{\i0\fs33} Or this will happen{\i1\fs40}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)\an8}僕が泣いているのは とても悔しいからです
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)\an8}Boku ga naite iru no wa totemo kuyashii kara desu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)}The reason I am crying is\Nbecause I am very frustrated
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}人の尊さやさしさ 踏みにじられそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Hito no toutosa yasashisa fuminijiraresou de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}I feel as though the nobility and\Nkindness of man is being trampled
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}力を示す者達は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Chikara o shimesu mono tachi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}しなやかさを失って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Shinayakasa o ushinatte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:34.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Those who show their strength lose their grace
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}ウソまみれドロまみれ じれったい風景でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uso-mamire doro-mamire jirettai fuukei desho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Covered in dirt and lies, isn't it a vexing sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}より強くしたたかに タフな生き方をしましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Yori tsuyoku shitataka ni tafu na ikikata o shimashou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's live more strongly, fiercely, and tougher
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}まっすぐ歩きましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Massugu arukimasho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's walk straight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.99,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}風は向かい風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.99,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kaze wa mukai kaze
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.99,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The wind is against us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:58.83,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ どけ どけ 後ろめたい奴はどけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:58.83,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke doke doke ushirometai yatsu wa doke
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:58.83,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, move, move, those with\Na guilty conscience, move aside
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.83,0:01:03.45,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}有象無象の町に 灯りをともせ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.83,0:01:03.45,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uzoumuzou no machi ni akari o tomose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.83,0:01:03.45,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Light up the town of riffraff
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:08.92,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ そこ どけ 真実のお通りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:08.92,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke soko doke shinjitsu no otouri da
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:08.92,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, make way, truth is coming through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}正義の時代がくるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Seigi no jidai ga kuru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The era of justice will come
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}希望の歌もあるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kibou no uta mo aru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}There are songs of hope too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.39,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}僕の命この世に 捧げてしまっていいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.39,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}Boku no inochi kono yo ni sasagete-shimatte ii sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.39,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)}I would happily sacrifice my life for this world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.15,0:01:35.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Takeshi Hokuto, 16 years old.\NHeir to the Hokuto Foundation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:37.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an8}His father is the chairman of the Hokuto Group
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:31.77,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\bord0.8\fs6\c&HFEFDFE&\fad(370,0)\t(\fs8)\move(358,412,358,412,0,1500)}Takeshi Hokuto (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.77,0:01:34.69,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\bord0.8\fs8\c&HFEFDFE&\t(\fs14)\move(358,412,358,411,0,2920)}Takeshi Hokuto (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.69,0:01:37.32,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\bord0.8\fs14\c&HFEFDFE&\t(\fs23)\move(358,411,358,407,0,2620)}Takeshi Hokuto (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.32,0:01:41.87,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\bord0.8\fs23\c&HFEFDFE&\t(\fs41)\move(358,407,358,397,0,4550)}Takeshi Hokuto (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:43.95,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\bord0.8\fs41\c&HFEFDFE&\t(\fs49)\move(358,397,358,393,0,2090)}Takeshi Hokuto (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.95,0:01:46.46,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\bord0.8\fs49\c&HFEFDFE&\t(\fs56)\move(358,393,358,389,0,2500)}Takeshi Hokuto (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:46.96,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\bord0.8\fs56\c&HFEFDFE&\t(\fs57)\move(358,389,358,388,0,500)}Takeshi Hokuto (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.96,0:01:48.37,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\bord0.8\fs57\c&HFEFDFE&\t(\fs59)\move(358,388,358,386,0,1420)}Takeshi Hokuto (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.37,0:01:50.59,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,350)\be2\bord0.8\fs59\c&HFEFDFE&\t(\fs60)\move(358,386,358,385,0,790)}Takeshi Hokuto (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.91,0:01:40.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an8}and also chairs the board of directors\Nof several high schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.49,0:01:44.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an8}His son, Takeshi, has controlled\Neighteen high schools
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.45,0:01:47.12,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an8}using his own force and his father's power as his weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.12,0:01:52.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an8}And at last, he transferred to Cromartie\NHigh School, known as the worst of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:54.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an8}to bring them into his clutches.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:56.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hokuto! Please wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:01:58.34,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad1.5\fnResurrection\fs44\be1\bord0.5\pos(362.532,340)\c&H2B25B7&}Empire of Ambition
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:02.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So this is Cromartie? \N Such a filthy place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.60,0:02:09.27,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(320,250)\pos(500.747,395)}Lackey
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.97,0:02:08.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}If there's someone who defies you,\Nlet's have him expelled right away,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:09.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,with your father's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.98,0:02:11.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,People are pigs!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.02,0:02:16.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'll hammer my ideals into the heads\Nof these incompetent pigs to control them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.32,0:02:17.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,First, we'll start here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.03,0:02:22.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I can handle this myself.\NYou wait for me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.08,0:02:22.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.25,0:02:28.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:31.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There was a guy who looked\N like a pro wrestler just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:33.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it was an illusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:36.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, this school is famous for its badasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.67,0:02:39.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, this guy's on a different level\Nthan badasses and delinquents!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:42.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,How can I describe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:44.89,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to be afraid of!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:48.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You've seen many badasses\Nup until now, right, Mr. Hokuto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:52.81,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, I've never seen anyone like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:54.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Please calm down, Mr. Hokuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:02:58.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If you stumble in a place like this,\Nyou won't be able to go forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:03:00.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:03.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But you see it with me as well this time! Promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:04.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:06.70,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Freddie, that's my seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:09.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You aren't even in our class!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:13.25,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Our class is next door, Kamiyama, Hayashida.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:16.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, Freddie. We were also mistaken\Nas to where our classroom was.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:22.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He was being slapped on the head for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:26.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm really surprised right now as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:28.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He just looks tough, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:29.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, that can't be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:31.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's camouflage to deceive us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:34.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:37.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If you don't like him, all you\Nhave to do is have him expelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:40.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What if he resents me for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:42.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You're more of a worrier\N than I thought, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:44.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But what worries me even more is that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:48.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling he'd still come to school even\Nafter being expelled, like nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:50.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, we can't do anything to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:52.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:57.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No matter how monstrous he may look,\Nhe's still just a human being like us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:03:59.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, you're exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:01.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Regardless of how he looks, \Nhe's just a human being like us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:04.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Now, let's open the door.\NHave some confidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:06.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay! Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:14.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's not a human being!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.15,0:04:17.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hello, Mommy? I can't go into the classroom.\NGet Daddy on the phone for me!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.52,0:04:20.32,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\c&HC239C0&\3c&H6D0E6C&\fnHand Drawn Shapes\frz2\shad0\blur0.5\bord1\fs52\pos(358,234)}T{\frz1.7}h{\frz1.5}e {\frz1.3}S{\frz1.1}t{\frz0.9}r{\frz0.7}i{\frz0.5}k{\frz0.3}e {\frz0.1}Ba{\frz-0.2}c{\frz-0.4}k {\frz-0.6}E{\frz-0.8}m{\frz-1.0}p{\frz-1.2}i{\frz-1.4}r{\frz-1.6}e
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:20.32,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\c&H852581&\3c&H5C2C40&\fnHand Drawn Shapes\frz2\shad0\blur0.3\bord1\fs51\pos(358,236)}T{\frz1.7}h{\frz1.5}e {\frz1.3}S{\frz1.1}t{\frz0.9}r{\frz0.7}i{\frz0.5}k{\frz0.3}e {\frz0.1}Ba{\frz-0.2}c{\frz-0.4}k {\frz-0.6}E{\frz-0.8}m{\frz-1}p{\frz-1.2}i{\frz-1.4}r{\frz-1.6}e
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:23.74,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Takenouchi, Freddie, that gorilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.74,0:04:27.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,These two guys and this animal\Nseem to command Year 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:30.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In short, all I need to do is\Nget control of them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:32.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, believe it or not, \Nthat's not really the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:33.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:35.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Actually, according to the information I have,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:39.55,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,it seems that the moves of these three\Nare centered around one man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:43.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see. Then that means that\NI just need to defeat that man, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:47.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No matter who he is, \Nhe'll be a piece of cake for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:49.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Just what kind of guy is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:51.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That man is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:53.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,...this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:54.35,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\bord0.6\be2\fs27\pos(237.911,396)}Main character Takashi Kamiyama
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:54.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:58.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I wondered what you were like.\NYou're just a worthless man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:05:00.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You'd better kneel down\Nin front of me immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:03.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Please hold on a second.\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.95,0:05:06.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully! My name is Takeshi Hokuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:08.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'll control this school too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:10.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,For the sake of my ideals!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:12.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Here comes another weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:16.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,As a first step, I've decided to bury you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:20.29,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?\N Do you think that such violence is allowed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:22.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Freddie wants a banana.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:25.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I guess the foolish masses can't understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:30.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,My father is the chair of this high school.\NHe can expel you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:31.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Can I say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:32.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:35.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This is a municipal school, so there's no chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:37.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? Municipal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:41.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In the first place, your uniform is different.\NThat's a white uniform, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:44.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:47.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I came to the wrong school. What'll I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:49.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I've already completed the transfer process,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:52.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,and it'd be very embarrassing\N to say I made a mistake this far into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:54.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I can't use Dad's power in this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:58.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But I've said this much, so I can't take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:00.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he's all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:00.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB7D2DC&}Okay, I've decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:01.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'll just use lies to cover it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:03.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, listen carefully, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:06.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,My dad isn't the chair of this school!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:09.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then what is he?\N You're not making sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:12.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You're the one who said he was the chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:14.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, hold on, my dad is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:18.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The evil mastermind who controls\N the Japanese government from the shadows,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:19.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,the Shadow Premier!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:20.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Mastermind?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:24.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,For my dad, it's easy to control a municipal\N high school from the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:26.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You bastards are also\Nnothing but his subordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:29.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Ouch, he did it. He's talking really crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:31.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Even elementary students\Nwouldn't believe such nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:33.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? ls that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:34.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:34.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:37.12,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,They bought it! These guys are total morons!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:40.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Even I'm getting confused as to what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:44.55,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So, what is the son of the evil one\Ndoing in a school like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:45.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Young master!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:48.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Son of the evil one?\N Oh, he's talking about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:49.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:52.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,To defeat that evil mastermind, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:54.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But the mastermind is your dad, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:56.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's right... Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:07:02.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,For a man, there is a time when he has to fight\Nfor justice, even if it's against his own father!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:03.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Can I say one thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:05.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Did he figure it out after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:08.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Please let me help you! For justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:09.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:12.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:14.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'd be upset if you forgot about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:16.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,About this Hayashida!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:18.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You dumbass! Of course\N you're our comrade too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:21.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay, now we have all the players.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:24.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,From today, we are comrades for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:27.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All right! Starting tomorrow, let's give it our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:28.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.33,0:07:33.34,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We're in deep trouble.
