Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:36.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Let's strum on a guitar in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.51,0:07:39.27,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\bord0.7\fnAnna\fs30\fscx124.62\c&HF7F9FB&}Eiji "New" Nonaka
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:42.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This has nothing to do with the story!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:46.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sixteen year old Takeshi Hokuto,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:50.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,who made an unheard of mistake\Nby transferring to the wrong school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:56.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He was driven into a difficult position due to\Nlies that he kept telling to hide that mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:08:01.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,To say the least, your father\N being the evil mastermind is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:04.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Stop it! When I think that was\Nwhat I said, I'm so embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:07.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But from how that story went,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:12.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,we now have to form a team with them\Nand fight against the evil mastermind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:15.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Think about it calmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:17.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,They're idiots who fell for a story like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:20.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,They're sure to have completely\Nforgotten about it after one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:23.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Truly, they were incredibly stupid, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:25.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,They're probably frolicking around somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:26.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Captain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:30.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,They've got a good memory\Nin spite of their stupidity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:32.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, we've looked all over for you, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:33.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Salute to our Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:35.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Where the hell did they buy those clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.87,0:08:40.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,They're certainly mistaken somehow,\NCaptain, I mean, Mr. Hokuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:41.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:42.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What the hell's that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:44.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm so embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:47.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Would you stop saying "Captain"\Nin front of everybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:48.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Why's that, Captain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:52.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This isn't good! They're serious.\NI'd better do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:55.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be good if we hang out\Nwith them any longer, Mr. Hokuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:58.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Besides, you're going to control\Nthis school, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:08:59.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I forgot about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:01.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see! Is this what they want?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:03.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Perhaps this is a trap meant to ensnare me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:06.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, it can't be. They're definitely stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:08.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Because their eyes are serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:11.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, I have no choice but to\Nevade the issue by feeding them more lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:12.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This looks pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:17.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Listen, everyone. The truth is,\N my dad found out about our troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:18.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?! The boss of our enemy did?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:21.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It seems that my dad, who's the\Nmastermind of the Japanese government,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:23.25,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,was so afraid of my existence
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:28.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,that he sent in an ex-Green Beret\Nfrom the US as an assassin to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:32.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy... He started his ridiculous talk again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:34.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,An assassin from the US?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:37.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Man, it looks like your dad is serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:38.34,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:39.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,They bought it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:44.18,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If I were with you any longer,\Nyou'd be involved too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:47.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So I've decided to leave our troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:48.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Nice! Good work, Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:53.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But if you quit, who the hell\Nis going to be our Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:54.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:56.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Kamiyama, I leave the rest to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:09:59.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But I don't know if I can play\Nsuch an important role.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:01.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:02.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hayashida...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:04.29,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You too, Freddie...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:07.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I understand. Follow me, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:08.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:09.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:14.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I can finally go home. I'm so exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:19.89,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I can't even imagine what will happen\N if I keep telling lies to those idiots from Cromartie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:24.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I can't stand it! Okay, I'll tell them\Nthe whole truth tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:25.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And I'll transfer schools again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:28.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:30.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:33.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We're going to spend our nights here\Nto protect you from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:39.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,As Captain, I can't let you die alone in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:42.53,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:44.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Things are getting crazier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:44.97,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\alpha130\fs24\fnNeon\bord0\c&H4E1728&\blur0.5\pos(346.671,139)}Next\N\N\N\NEpisode
