Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:49.98,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fs26\blur0.6\fnArial Black\bord3.2\c&H000000&\3c&H3F3F3F&\pos(203.924,50)}Sakigake!!\NCromartie High School
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:49.98,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Black\shad0\fs36\bord2.2\blur0.5\pos(492.816,390)}Next Episode, Pootan
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:37.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:39.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sakigake!! Cromartie High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:42.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I thought about many things, but you\Ncan't predict what happens in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:44.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You can't predict what happens\Nin the next episode either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:47.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Could it be there's an idiot among us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:49.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Who are you talking about?
